# langbot-plugin-sdk

## Connection

### with LangBot

- Stdio
    - Passively
- WebSocket
    - Server: `:5400 /control/ws`

### with Plugins

- Stdio
    - Actively
- WebSocket (Debug)
    - Server: `:5401 /debug/ws`